name: France NFT. Yellow Beryl
description: Unique NFT country France. In a single copy. The base is made of precious Yellow Beryl, cut from Purple opal. It holds its most recognizable architectural landmark in Paris, the Eiffel Tower, made of gold and silver. A stand made of pearls, with the help of a mechanism, a couple in love moves along the trajectory. In the corners there are 4 recognizable "symbols" of France: A Rooster (the national symbol of France), Cheese (one of the most famous in the world), Perfume (the famous French perfume) and a Hanger (France-the heart of fashion)
